body_html: Try cleaning out your caches and trying a fresh rebuild (start from scratch in a new directory). Transient failures of git fetches have been known to happen if ssl certificates temporarily get out of whack. Let us know if that doesn't fix it. (can't find the issue where I saw this before at the moment)
